" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 547px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Follicular lymphoma: bcl-2 staining",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 527px; height: 288px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Left panel: Neoplastic cells within the lymph node follicle from a patient with follicular lymphoma show strong immunostaining (brown color) for bcl-2. The lymphocytes in the thin mantles and the interfollicular regions also show bcl-2 reactivity. Right panel: In comparison, the germinal centers in a reactive follicle are bcl-2 negative, with the positive cells being located in the mantle and interfollicular regions.",
